    <title>Week3-8937</title>
    <link href="/2025/10/31/Week3-8937/"/>
    <url>/2025/10/31/Week3-8937/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="前置知识：前缀和"><a href="#前置知识：前缀和" class="headerlink" title="前置知识：前缀和"></a>前置知识：前缀和</h1><h2 id="基础认识"><a href="#基础认识" class="headerlink" title="基础认识:"></a>基础认识:</h2><ul><li><p>前缀和是什么</p><p> 可以简单理解为 数列的前 𝑛 项的和</p></li><li><p>前缀和有什么用</p><p>  用于快速求解区间和</p></li><li><p>前缀和的地位</p><p>  是一种重要的预处理思想</p></li></ul><h2 id="一维前缀和"><a href="#一维前缀和" class="headerlink" title="一维前缀和"></a>一维前缀和</h2><p>对于长度为 $n$ 的数列 {$a_i$}, 如果要多次查询区间 $[l, r]$ 的所有数字之和，就可以考虑使用前缀和。</p><h3 id="递推式"><a href="#递推式" class="headerlink" title="递推式"></a>递推式</h3><p>$s_0 &#x3D; 0$</p><p>$s_i &#x3D; s_{i-1} + a_i$</p><p>是不是很像高中学的数列前 $n$ 项和 $s_n$</p><h3 id="查询"><a href="#查询" class="headerlink" title="查询"></a>查询</h3><p>现在假设我们需要查询 $[l,r]$ 之间数的和，就可以使用公式 $s_r - s_{l-1}$ 来计算区间和。</p><h3 id="对比"><a href="#对比" class="headerlink" title="对比"></a>对比</h3><p>因此，我们便可以在 $O(1)$ 的时间查询到区间 $[l,r]$ 的和，代价是我们需要 $O(n)$ 的时间进行计算所有 $n$ 的前缀和。</p><p>示例：对于 $m$ 个查询区间 $[l,r]$。<br>如果采用暴力算法，对每个区间进行遍历求和，时间复杂度为 $O(m*n)$</p><p>但是用前缀和优化查询，时间复杂度为 $O(n+m)$</p><p>这么对比能大概 get 到前缀和的用途了吗？</p><blockquote><p>这里看不懂 $O(…)$ 是什么可以留个概念，有这么个玩意，等之后老师讲，或者直接问学长。</p></blockquote><h1 id="具体思路"><a href="#具体思路" class="headerlink" title="具体思路"></a>具体思路</h1><p>上面解释了前缀和的基础知识。相信你已经对这道题有了一定的思路了。</p><p>假如你因为不了解前缀和而写不出来，可以暂停阅读，想一想前缀和应该怎么应用到这道题上。</p><p>如果还是没什么思路，就跟着我下面的来看看这道题。</p><h2 id="题意分析"><a href="#题意分析" class="headerlink" title="题意分析"></a>题意分析</h2><p>题目要求一个数列被分成两半后，左右两边和的差值的最小值。</p><p>注意到要求和</p><h2 id="最直观的想法，暴力"><a href="#最直观的想法，暴力" class="headerlink" title="最直观的想法，暴力"></a>最直观的想法，暴力</h2><p>简单来说，我们可以假设每两个数之间被切一刀，然后数组被分成两半，然后我们计算两边的和的差值，更新最小值即可。</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>( <span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">1</span>; i &lt;= n; ++ i ) </span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> left = <span class="number">0</span>, right = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>( <span class="type">int</span> j = <span class="number">1</span>; j &lt;= i; ++ j ) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        left += a[i];</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>( <span class="type">int</span> j = i<span class="number">+1</span>; j &lt;= n; ++ j ) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        right += a[i];</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> diff = <span class="built_in">abs</span>( left - right );</span><br><span class="line">    ans = <span class="built_in">min</span>( ans, diff );</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>但是这种写法无疑会暴力运算每一个区间，最终的时间复杂度为 $O(n^2)$。</p><p>对于这题 $n\leq1e5$ 来说，最终时间为 $1e10$ 超过了 $1s$ 时间限制的 $1e8$ 的数据处理量。</p><blockquote><p>$1e5&#x3D;10^5$ 科学技术法 方便书写</p><p>一般来说，计算机 $1s$ 能执行 $1e8$ 的数据处理。</p><p>所以对于输入数据的规模，我们需要找到不同时间复杂度的算法来解决问题。</p><p>这就是算法的应用，你理解了吗？</p></blockquote><p>因此，我们需要一个更加优秀的算法解决这个问题。</p><h2 id="不难想到的优化，前缀和"><a href="#不难想到的优化，前缀和" class="headerlink" title="不难想到的优化，前缀和"></a>不难想到的优化，前缀和</h2><p>根据之前对题目的分析，我们发现，其实我们每次对 $[1,j]$ 以及 $[j+1,n]$ 两个区间的求和占据了很多时间，而这种区间求和，我们则可以使用前缀和来优化。</p><p>不难想到 </p><p>区间 $[1,j]$ 的和即 $s_j-s_{0}$</p><p>区间 $[j+1,n]$ 的和即 $s_n-s_{j}$</p><p>所以如果我们对每个位置进行判断该不该切一刀，每次只需要用两个算式计算两边大小就行，不用每个求和过去，</p><p>这样的话，时间复杂度就是 $O(n * 2)$。</p><p>因为复杂度可以消去常数，所以理论上就是 $O(n)$。</p><p>对于这道 $1e5$ 的 $n$ ，完全足以胜任。</p><p>以下是代码实现</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>( <span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">1</span>; i &lt;= n; ++ +i ) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    sum[i] = sum[i<span class="number">-1</span>] + a[i];</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> ans = <span class="number">1e9</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>( <span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">1</span>; i &lt;= n; ++ i ) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> left = sum[i] - sum[<span class="number">0</span>];</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> right = sum[n] - sum[i];</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> diff = <span class="built_in">abs</span>( left - right );</span><br><span class="line">    ans = <span class="built_in">min</span>( ans, diff );  </span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="不过这题还没结束"><a href="#不过这题还没结束" class="headerlink" title="不过这题还没结束"></a>不过这题还没结束</h3><p>还有一个隐藏陷阱，注意到 $a\leq1e5$，并且$n\leq1e5$。</p><p>所以，极端情况下，我们会处理到的区间和最大为 $n<em>a$，大小为$1e5</em>1e5&#x3D;1e10$。</p><p>而我们的 $int$ 整数类型只能存 $2^{31}-1$ 也就是差不多 $1e9$ 的数字。</p><p>所以，我们还需要使用 $long long$ 来存储数据。</p><p>最后给出ac代码</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span><span class="string">&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 上面的头文件不用管，c++写法</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">const</span> <span class="type">int</span> maxn = <span class="number">1e5</span> + <span class="number">50</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 此处表示定义maxn为一个常量</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 常量即一个不可修改的值</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 所以是静态的数据，可以用来定义数组大小</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 还有一个注意点，因为数组是从0开始计数的</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 所以如果刚刚好开 1e5 的大小，第 1e5 个数字会无法访问到。</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">long</span> <span class="type">long</span> a[maxn];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">long</span> <span class="type">long</span> sum[maxn];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 这里用maxn定义大小方便</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 如果每次修改大小，只需要修改上面的值</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 不用对每一个数组大小进行修改</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> n;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;%d&quot;</span>, &amp;n);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 输入</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>( <span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">1</span>; i &lt;= n; ++ i ) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;%d&quot;</span>, &amp;a[i]);</span><br><span class="line">        sum[i] = sum[i<span class="number">-1</span>] + a[i];</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 初始化</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">long</span> <span class="type">long</span> ans = <span class="number">1e18</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>( <span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">1</span>; i &lt;= n; ++ i ) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">long</span> <span class="type">long</span> left = sum[i];</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">long</span> <span class="type">long</span> right = sum[n] - sum[i];</span><br><span class="line">        ans = <span class="built_in">min</span>( ans, <span class="built_in">abs</span>( left - right ) );</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 数据处理</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;%lld\n&quot;</span>, ans);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 输出部分</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>很感谢你能看到这里，愿你在 ac 过程中不断成长，每一次提交都能学到一点新东西。</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
